    }}>{`✏️ Design fundamentals: 7 tricks graphic designers don’t want you to know`}</h1>
    <blockquote>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`A poorly planned talk by Scott Blissett – May 8, 2018
`}<img alt="Design fundamentals" src="https://d2mxuefqeaa7sj.cloudfront.net/s_5594818096833C98BE67E017D04B0A135886FB67175E3EC47DE614BB14E75EC7_1525748404437_Slack_-_Present_Company.jpg" /></p>
